    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336300/extras/908f258c60504b034b8450773dd8109b.avif?t=1754669913\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336300/extras_big/908f258c60504b034b8450773dd8109b.avif?t=1754669913 width=800 height=208 /></span><strong>Welcome to the Koshari Defense Demo! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious creatures are attacking the empire! The pharaoh needs you to build a defense to defeat them.   You must channel the divine power to retake your temples and build towers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this demo you can get to know the world of Koshari Defense in a few selected levels. Fight your way through various regions in Koshari's kingdom.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>We appreciate your feedback!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We decided to release our game as a demo to listen to your feedback during the development. Feel free to share your thoughts on the game via our support email!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Place towers and connect them to the palace via power lines</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336300/extras/42e9acadf43877f527632b400188c041.apng?t=1754669913\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336300/extras/42e9acadf43877f527632b400188c041.poster.avif?t=1754669913\" class=\"bb_img\" width=192 height=288 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade towers to improve their abilities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336300/extras/2795f55af5e641d202e1baf8b37bcf65.apng?t=1754669913\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336300/extras/2795f55af5e641d202e1baf8b37bcf65.poster.avif?t=1754669913\" class=\"bb_img\" width=192 height=288 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Retake temples to gain extra resources each wave</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336300/extras/e5573f4a5a4414e62d0fc44efbfa93e5.poster.avif?t=1754669913\" width=512 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336300/extras/e5573f4a5a4414e62d0fc44efbfa93e5.webm?t=1754669913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
